    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Feature already in Vim?\n\n_No response_\n\n### Feature description\n\nWhile `nvim_get_option` and `nvim_buf_get_option` can return individual option values, I think it would make sense if `vim.opt`/`vim.opt_local` could mimic the behaviour of `:set` and `:setlocal` and return the global/local settings (as a table).\r\nTrying to parse the msg output is clumsy and it would be nice if the results could be returned as a table.",
